Configure sampling settings
Use extension methods of TelemetryProcessorChainBuilder as shown below to customize sampling behavior.

 Important

If you use this method to configure sampling, please make sure to set the aiOptions.EnableAdaptiveSampling property to false when calling AddApplicationInsightsTelemetry(). After making this change, you then need to follow the instructions in the code block below exactly in order to re-enable adaptive sampling with your customizations in place. Failure to do so can result in excess data ingestion. Always test post changing sampling settings, and set an appropriate daily data cap to help control your costs.

builder.Services.AddApplicationInsightsTelemetry(new ApplicationInsightsServiceOptions
{
 EnableAdaptiveSampling = false,
});
